            "title": "盤中速報 - 華納兄弟探索(WBD-US)大漲5.37%，報9.02美元",
            "description": "<main class=\"c1tt5pk2\" id=\"article-container\" style=\"--c1tt5pk2-0:20px\"><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>華納兄弟探索(<a data-ga-click-item=\"USS:WBD:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/usstock/detail/WBD\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">WBD-US</a>)截至台北時間08日22:00股價上漲0.46美元，報9.02美元，漲幅5.37%，成交量18,061,094（股），盤中最高價9.04美元、最低價8.06美元。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p><em>美股指數盤中表現</em></p></section><section style=\"margin-top:20px\"><ul><li><a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/GI/DJI\">道瓊指數</a>：+0.49%</li><li><a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/GI/INX\">S&amp;P 500</a>指數：+0.5%</li><li><a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/GI/IXIC\">NASDAQ</a>指數：+0.75%</li><li><a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/GI/SOX\">費城半導體</a>指數：+0.87%</li></ul></section><section><p><em>華納兄弟探索(<a data-ga-click-item=\"USS:WBD:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/usstock/detail/WBD\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">WBD-US</a>)歷史漲跌幅</em></p></section><!--$--><!--/$--><section style=\"margin-top:20px\"><ul> <li>近 1 週：-1.27%</li> <li>近 1 月：+5.81%</li> <li>近 3 月：-15.75%</li> <li>近 6 月：-8.64%</li> <li>今年以來：-19.02%</li></ul></section></main>",
